metatags.og:description:
Creative Partner and Founder of Interstate, London, Bahrain, Milan. · Creative Partner and Founder of Interstate, London, Bahrain, Milan.
I have thirty years experience in creative direction, strategic thinking and graphic design for brand experience, identity, packaging, and interactive media. 
As a designer, I’m a visual librarian who’s passionate about design, art, culture and nature, and always looking for ideas that last and help human journeying. 
My specialist knowledge is in all things automotive, from major OEMs to electric racing, the future of mobility and how design relates to that. 
I have over 15 years experience of working in the Middle East, with a particular interest in Arabic typeface, design and culture. 

Being Suffolk born, London raised, and Denmark wed, I like contrasts as much as I like wide skies and broad horizons. 

And always keep my eyes on the prize.  · Experience: Interstate · Education: Canterbury College of Art · Location: London · 500+ connections on LinkedIn. View N
